# NOTICE

PlayerKit links FFmpeg, which is distributed under the LGPL v2.1+ license.

- FFmpeg source: https://ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-8.1.2.tar.gz
- Build script: scripts/build_ffmpeg.sh (generates the xcframeworks in Sources/CFFmpeg/xcframeworks/)

## Replacing FFmpeg Libraries

To comply with LGPL, you must be able to replace the FFmpeg libraries with your own build:

1. Clone this repository.
2. Run `scripts/build_ffmpeg.sh` with your custom FFmpeg configuration.
3. Replace the contents of `Sources/CFFmpeg/xcframeworks/` with the output.
4. Rebuild your application.

## Bundled Libraries

The following FFmpeg libraries are bundled as xcframeworks:

- libavcodec (LGPL v2.1+)
- libavformat (LGPL v2.1+)
- libavutil (LGPL v2.1+)
- libswresample (LGPL v2.1+)
- libswscale (LGPL v2.1+)
